::Aerotaur::
    The missile lands in front of him and knocks him backwards across the 
ground.  "Ah, bloody hells.  (And yes I do mean all of them.)  This is 
starting to get me annoyed."  He takes of into the air toward Unitron.  
"LEAVE US THE HELL ALONE!!!!!"  He fires four shots with his left arm cannon 
at Unitron.  With his right hand he draws his staff and leads with one of the 
blades, attempting to impale Unitron.
